{"tid":956721,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【刀法爐火純青!!】6GB / 4GB / 3GB 容量齊備，NVIDIA RTX 2060 一系列型號曝光！","createTime":"2018-12-26T13:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T10:59:11.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1262ac3734e0e2412c0a0b3a0434f04d5c2d4b6d","tid":956721,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/17567/刀法爐火純青6GB4GB3GB_容量齊備_NVIDIA_RTX_2060_一系列型號曝光\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F17567%2F%E5%88%80%E6%B3%95%E7%88%90%E7%81%AB%E7%B4%94%E9%9D%926GB4GB3GB_%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E9%BD%8A%E5%82%99_NVIDIA_RTX_2060_%E4%B8%80%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E5%9E%8B%E8%99%9F%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89&d=pJzRYsdkl93uV2yzkgrKUcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ac4bf746\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/17567/刀法爐火純青6GB4GB3GB_容量齊備_NVIDIA_RTX_2060_一系列型號曝光</a><br />\n<br />\n不少傳言都指 NVIDIA 將會在即將舉行的 CES 2019 大會上發佈主流級的 GeForce RTX 2060 繪圖卡，雖然官方未有確認，但近來有不少關於 RTX 2060 的爆料流出，看來這款新卡的推出時間已經非常接近，最新有外媒就再進一步找到RTX 2060 更多的資料，在 ECC 認證庫中發現到三十幾款型號，當中在 GDDR6 及 GDDR5X 兩種不同速率將會有 6GB、4GB、3GB 的記憶體容量，可見 RTX 2060 很大機會將會提供幾個版本的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file.hkepc.net/2018/12/source/26154032321342385886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2018%2F12%2Fsource%2F26154032321342385886.jpg&h=8cac808b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n根據 ECC 歐亞經濟委員會認證庫中的資料顯示，GIGABYTE 一共提交了多達 39 款的 RTX 2060 繪圖卡型號，分別為 6GB 記憶體容量的 GDDR6 / GDDR5(X) 產品、4GB 記憶體容量 GDDR6 / GDDR5(X) 產品、3GB 記憶體容量的 GDDR6 / GDDR5(X) 產品，並將會備有 AORUS、GAMING OC、WindForce、Turbo、mini ITX等系列。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file.hkepc.net/2018/12/source/26154031311295389035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2018%2F12%2Fsource%2F26154031311295389035.jpg&h=eb3f1273&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"38a870e75ea5c1b8bf54f1c7c6508319cb44f8f0","tid":956721,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"至於規格方面，之前的消息確認 RTX 2060 將會基於 TU106 繪圖核心，擁有 1920 個CUDA Core，並在已獲得繪圖卡識別工具 GPU-Z 的支援，同時在《Final Fantasy XV》的跑分數據更顯示 RTX 2060 在 4K 解像度下比 GTX 1060 6GB 提高了高達 30% 的效能，至於與 GTX 1070 僅相差 6% 左右，可見 RTX 2060 有不錯的性能提升。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://file.hkepc.net/2018/12/source/18202940801474916932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2018%2F12%2Fsource%2F18202940801474916932.jpg&h=042538ba&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"551693bd924d8e4026f5f348a6db144a311b142b","tid":956721,"uid":223077,"like":0,"dislike":44,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"611835cbeb32d242b5c3faa527885d7d882fefb2","tid":956721,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"></span>"},{"pid":"52e006e8525942e5571ca8c10b0bcde17ee51467","tid":956721,"uid":76705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"551693bd924d8e4026f5f348a6db144a311b142b","tid":956721,"uid":223077,"like":0,"dislike":44,"score":-44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">屌柒Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，歡迎干擾Xboxone Contana 留名系統運作。</code></pre>"}]}